data.description: Somerset Lake Lifestyle with almost 2 acres of lakefront living. This charming lake home has incredible charm and stunning modern updates that creates a perfect combination. Enjoy the beautiful wide plank pine hardwood flooring in this hillside retreat with bedrooms on the main level and a “knock your socks off” lower level with open entertaining kitchen with new white cabinetry and stainless appliances. Live in a grand way with views of the lake and sunsets from the main bedroom balcony and deck of this pampered home with detached 763 sq ft guest house with loft and detached two car garage for additional storage. The guest house has great sleeping area and is comfortable for spill over entertaining. Somerset Lake is the perfect quiet retreat just approximately 15 minutes east of Bloomington and 15 minutes west of the Village of Nashville. Lake covenants do not allow gas powered motors on the lake, but is perfect for low-key lake relaxation. Home includes a dock as well as the small 2020 pontoon boat. **This location is serviced by SCI Fiber.**
